Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.54,0:17:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來你們真要闖進\N那片槍林彈雨當中嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.84,0:17:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，這是工作嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一個來了，過來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，馬上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.78,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心點哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.58,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回程我們還會再過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.72,0:17:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾，今天內我們也要到\N諾齊亞避難去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯維拉號傳來報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.60,0:17:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擊破敵方槍兵百分之15
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.87,0:17:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓋柏格號輕微損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.87,0:17:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方槍兵損傷超過三成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經超過公會的規定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前戰況我方佔壓倒性的優勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.24,0:18:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要發出停戰勸說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.63,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜一點，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把注意力集中在儀表板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵方拒絕停戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,槍兵隊退下，改用砲擊戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.08,0:19:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特公會的\N克勞地亞組件脫離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯戰艦三艘沈沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方艦隊勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.17,0:19:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架先鋒艇要求登艦許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.31,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸給我聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.68,0:19:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有書信要交付旗艦克勞索拉斯\N艦長大衛‧麥德賽大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.48,0:19:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是諾齊亞先鋒艇組織所屬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.05,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士‧沃卡以及拉薇‧海德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.79,0:20:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,登艦許可下來了\N從後方甲板登艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走囉，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.17,0:20:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,技術不差哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.58,0:20:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是克勞士‧沃卡\N感謝允許我們登艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是拉薇‧海德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.05,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…你們贏了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.49,0:20:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然\N我們麥德賽艦隊大獲全勝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,錯了，走右邊啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑪達號！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.38,0:21:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.39,0:21:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告損傷情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.69,0:21:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特梅雷亞號中彈沈沒中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.78,0:21:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是度西斯的殘餘艦隊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.51,0:21:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是，從上空出現了\N未經登記的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是違反協定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安斯維拉號失去航行能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.72,0:21:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基爾特公會在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.24,0:21:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士精神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.94,0:21:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.71,0:22:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說大獲全勝嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，難道不是嗎
